NimDecl[N] = object
  case kind*: NimDeclKind
  of nekProcDecl:
      procdecl*: ProcDecl[N]

  of nekEnumDecl:
      enumdecl*: EnumDecl[N]

  of nekObjectDecl:
      objectdecl*: ObjectDecl[N]

  of nekAliasDecl:
      aliasDecl*: AliasDecl[N]

  of nekPassthroughCode:
      passIInfo*: LineInfo
      passthrough*: N

  of nekMultitype:
      typedecls*: seq[NimTypeDecl[N]]

  of nekFieldDecl:
      fieldDecl*: ObjectField[N]
  Source   Edit

NimTypeDecl[N] = object
  case kind*: NimTypeDeclKind
  of ntdkEnumDecl:

  of ntdkObjectDecl:

  of ntdkAliasDecl:
